            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Julius Klüver</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#kluverJ" start="538.117" end="x">To the best of my knowledge the Canadians have rendered in this war mostly labor service. Only a few joined the army or navy.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
